85
00:05:15,659 --> 00:05:17,630
<font color=#FFFF00>Tunggu sebentar.</font>

86
00:05:18,370 --> 00:05:21,070
<font color=#FFFF00>Young Hye, kau
punya kelainan?</font>

87
00:05:21,570 --> 00:05:23,940
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau secara berkala menuntut...</font>

88
00:05:23,940 --> 00:05:28,080
<font color=#FFFF00>untuk bercerai, mengakhiri
