114
00:06:30,310 --> 00:06:32,409
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayah sudah kesal.</font>

115
00:06:32,409 --> 00:06:34,179
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan berkata begitu.</font>

116
00:06:34,179 --> 00:06:35,609
<font color=#FFFF00>Ibu tidak melakukan kesalahan.</font>

117
00:06:35,609 --> 00:06:37,380
<font color=#FFFF00>Ibu sudah bertahan
begitu lama.</font>

118
00:06:37,380 --> 00:06:39,049
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak bisakah kalian
tidak bertengkar?</font>

119
00:06:39,049 --> 00:06:41,080
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku takut.</font>

120
00:06:47,320 --> 00:06:50,529
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau akan melupakan
semuanya besok.</font>

121
00:06:51,429 --> 00:06:54,560
<font color=#FFFF00>Omo. Apa yang terjadi?</font>

122
00:06:54,630 --> 00:06:57,529
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa ada mobil
