123
00:06:57,599 --> 00:06:58,729
<font color=#FFFF00>Dimana?</font>

124
00:07:00,799 --> 00:07:02,200
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku takut.</font>

125
00:07:02,739 --> 00:07:06,909
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang terjadi? Kenapa banyak sekali
