126
00:07:06,909 --> 00:07:09,010
<font color=#FFFF00>Pak Kim, arahkan
mobil ke sana.</font>

127
00:07:14,279 --> 00:07:18,020
<font color=#FFFF00>Permisi? Pak Polisi.</font>

128
00:07:18,219 --> 00:07:20,820
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa terjadi kecelakaan
