131
00:07:27,599 --> 00:07:28,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Kami sedang mencarinya.</font>

132
00:07:28,760 --> 00:07:29,969
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya Tuhan.</font>

133
00:07:30,229 --> 00:07:34,400
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa ada pencuri di
lingkungan mewah ini?</font>

134
00:07:34,539 --> 00:07:36,669
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimanapun,
selamat bertugas.</font>

135
00:07:36,669 --> 00:07:38,339
<font color=#FFFF00>Kami akan segera menangkapnya. Jangan khawatir.</font>

136
00:07:38,339 --> 00:07:39,440
<font color=#FFFF00>Tunggu sebentar.</font>

137
00:07:40,310 --> 00:07:41,580
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini tip.</font>

138
00:07:41,580 --> 00:07:44,049
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang sedang Anda lakukan?
Saya tidak boleh menerimanya.</font>

139
00:07:44,210 --> 00:07:45,750
<font color=#FFFF00>Oke.</font>

140
00:07:45,950 --> 00:07:47,650
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia tidak mau tip.</font>

141
00:07:48,080 --> 00:07:49,419
<font color=#FFFF00>Selamat bertugas.</font>

142
00:07:50,289 --> 00:07:51,789
<font color=#FFFF00>- Ibu.
- Kenapa?</font>

143
00:07:51,789 --> 00:07:54,419
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini sedikit seram.</font>

144
00:07:54,419 --> 00:07:57,159
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan khawatir. Kita sudah
memasang sistem keamanan.</font>

145
00:07:57,159 --> 00:07:59,159
<font color=#FFFF00>Polisi akan datang dalam
waktu satu menit.</font>

146
00:08:00,000 --> 00:08:02,200
<font color=#FFFF00>Sistem keamanan?
Baik, ayo pergi.</font>

147
00:08:06,500 --> 00:08:09,570
<font color=#FFFF00>Aigoo. Aku bosan
dengan pola ini.</font>

148
00:08:09,570 --> 00:08:11,010
<font color=#FFFF00>Bukankah kau bosan
dengan ini?</font>

149
00:08:11,210 --> 00:08:13,510
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau selalu berkemas
dan membongkar barang.</font>

150
00:08:13,839 --> 00:08:15,609
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa itu menghiburmu?</font>

151
00:08:17,710 --> 00:08:20,620
<font color=#FFFF00>Baik. Aku tidak tahu
kenapa kau kesal,</font>

152
00:08:20,620 --> 00:08:23,650
<font color=#FFFF00>tapi itu semua salahku.
Hentikan saja.</font>

153
00:08:25,919 --> 00:08:27,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa menurutmu
aku hanya kesal?</font>

154
00:08:28,260 --> 00:08:30,159
<font color=#FFFF00>Itulah mengapa kau
tidak cocok denganku.</font>

155
00:08:30,630 --> 00:08:31,929
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa? Aku?</font>

156
00:08:32,859 --> 00:08:35,029
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau berbicara tentangku?</font>

157
00:08:35,130 --> 00:08:37,000
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, aku sedang
berbicara tentangmu.</font>

158
00:08:37,370 --> 00:08:39,169
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau selalu berbicara
kasar denganku.</font>

159
00:08:39,169 --> 00:08:40,939
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa aku tidak bisa
berbicara kasar denganmu?</font>

160
00:08:40,939 --> 00:08:43,439
<font color=#FFFF00>- Hong Young Hye.
- Kenapa Lee Shin Mo?</font>

161
00:08:45,510 --> 00:08:47,640
<font color=#FFFF00>- Ibu.
- Tenanglah.</font>

162
00:08:48,579 --> 00:08:50,279
<font color=#FFFF00>Minggir. Jangan bergerak.</font>

163
00:08:50,850 --> 00:08:53,480
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika kau terus melakukan ini,
