165
00:08:55,620 --> 00:08:57,020
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan bangunkan
singa yang tidur.</font>

166
00:08:57,689 --> 00:08:59,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Singa? Kau pasti bercanda.</font>

167
00:09:00,319 --> 00:09:02,260
<font color=#FFFF00>- Hei.
- Ayah.</font>

168
00:09:03,789 --> 00:09:07,500
<font color=#FFFF00>Baik, aku akan berhenti
karena So Won.</font>

169
00:09:07,900 --> 00:09:11,829
<font color=#FFFF00>Mari kita bicara, karena kau
